{"tid":266818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎恐襲殉職男警與在世男友冥婚　奧朗德出席儀式","createTime":"2017-06-01T18:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T00:01:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9848d1aabf27c9cabb843637c8c0a12cca0dce","tid":266818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T18:29:23.000Z","msg":"2017-06-01 11:57<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170601/_2017060112100378832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170601%2F_2017060112100378832.jpg&h=7f477ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">37歲殉職男警員朱格利（右）獲安排與在世男伴卡爾迪斯舉行冥婚。</span><br />\n今年4月在法國巴黎香榭麗舍大道恐襲中，頭部中槍殉職的37歲男警朱格利（Xavier Jugele），獲安排與他在世的同性伴侶舉行冥婚儀式。法國前總統奧朗德和巴黎女市長伊達爾戈都應邀出席。<br />\n<br />\n朱格利生前一向積極為同性戀者爭取權益。他和男伴卡爾迪斯（Etienne Cardiles）一向只是同居，沒有領養孩子。他們周二獲安排在市長辦公室舉行冥婚儀式，部分官員出席。<br />\n<br />\n法國現行法例容許冥婚，是世界上少數容許冥婚的國家之一。當日舉行的，相信是法國歷來第一宗冥婚儀式。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月20日，朱格利在巴黎香榭麗舍大道當值時被一名男子開槍擊斃。另有兩名警員受傷。疑兇其後被警員殺死。調查人員在疑兇身旁找到一張提及極端組織伊斯蘭國的字條。當局其後定性該宗事件為恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n朱格利遇害後，卡爾迪斯曾發表一篇激動人心的講話，稱：「我沒有仇恨，朱格利，因為你不是一個帶着仇恨的人。仇恨不造就你的心跳，也不造就你成為和平使者。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/917055/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F917055%2F&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=65b3b1c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F917055%2F&h=e54430f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/917055/</a>"},{"pid":"1e4adc9cc6685ab375ce0ad704c2b0f795a5437c","tid":266818,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T21:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48052ec090c83aa45b0d6abbb6224ccc7f229c66","tid":266818,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8668f84d14f593b8c0bbcb2ea79762f9ca47dfb","tid":266818,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://progressiveredneckpreacher.files.wordpress.com/2015/05/sourgrapes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprogressiveredneckpreacher.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F05%2Fsourgrapes.jpg&h=979a35ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}